OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry start
OL,6,Fthen cloud thickening to bring a
OL,7,Flittle rain at times later in the
OL,8,Fevening. Then the rest of the night
OL,9,Fwill be dry with clear periods but
OL,10,Fsome rain into western Tayside towards
OL,11,Fdawn.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTuesday:FCloudy with some mostly light
OL,14,Frain at times, though parts of the
OL,15,Feast coast will stay dry. Some heavier
OL,16,Frain later in the evening, with strong
OL,17,Fwinds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
